sql_statement.static: Round((TxRes.FrameCount/genCon.Duration),3) AS 'OfferedLoadFps', Round((RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)),3) AS 'ForwardingRateFps', Round((TxRes.L1BitCount/genCon.Duration/(((genCon.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / genCon.PercentageLoad)*1000000))*100, 3) as OfferedLoadPercent, Round(genCon.PercentageLoad,3) as 'IntendedLoadPercent', TxRes.FrameCount as 'TxFrameCount', TxRes.FrameCount as 'ExpectedFrames', RxRes.FrameCount as 'RxFrameCount', RxRes.DroppedFrameCount as 'FramesLost', case when Round((RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)),3) = 0 then 'NA' when (Round((RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)),3) - Round((TxRes.FrameCount/genCon.Duration),3)) > 1 then 'True' else 'False' end as ForwardPressure FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb JOIN GeneratorPortResults AS GenPortRes JOIN GeneratorConfig AS genCon ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND GenPortRes.ParentPort = Sb.ParentHnd AND GenPortRes.ParentHnd = genCon.ParentHnd

columns: TrialNum, FrameSize, InterFrameGap, Duration, ExpectedMinimumIFG, TxFrameCount, ExpectedFrames, RxFrameCount, FramesLost, ForwardPressure, IntendedLoadPercent, OfferedLoadPercent, ForwardingRateFps, OfferedLoadFps

sql_statement.static: Round((TxRes.FrameCount/genCon.Duration),3) AS 'OfferedLoadFps',  Round((TxRes.L1BitCount/genCon.Duration/(((genCon.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / genCon.PercentageLoad)*1000000))*100, 3) as OfferedLoadPercent, Round(genCon.PercentageLoad,3) as 'IntendedLoadPercent', TxRes.FrameCount as 'TxFrameCount', TxRes.FrameCount as 'ExpectedFrames', TxRes.FrameCount as 'FramesLost', 'NA' as 'ForwardPressure' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb JOIN GeneratorPortResults AS GenPortRes JOIN GeneratorConfig AS genCon ON TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND GenPortRes.ParentPort = Sb.ParentHnd AND GenPortRes.ParentHnd = genCon.ParentHnd

columns: TrialNum, FrameSize, InterFrameGap, Duration, ExpectedMinimumIFG, TxFrameCount, ExpectedFrames, RxFrameCount, FramesLost, IntendedLoadPercent, OfferedLoadPercent, ForwardingRateFps, OfferedLoadFps, ForwardPressure

sql_statement.static: insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Number of trials', (select cast(MaxVal as int) from spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand where ParentHnd = (select Handle from spirent_methodology_IterationWhileCommand where IterationName = 'Trial')))
insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Trial Duration (s)', (select Value from spirent_methodology_setPropertyCommand where PropertyName = 'Duration'))

insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Frame Sizes (bytes)', (select replace(ValueList, ' ', ',') from spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand where ParentHnd = (select Handle from spirent_methodology_IterationWhileCommand where IterationName = 'FrameSize')))
insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Ingress Inter-frame Gap (bytes)', (select Value from spirent_methodology_setPropertyCommand where PropertyName = 'FixedLoad'))
insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Start traffic delay (s)', (select WaitTime from WaitCommand where Name = 'Start Traffic Delay'))
insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Wait after traffic stopped (s)', (select WaitTime from WaitCommand where Name = 'Wait after traffic stopped'))
insert into MethRfc2889FPConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Threshold minimum Inter-frame gap (bytes)', (select Value from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where Name = 'Set threshold'))
select Parameter as 'Parameter', Value as 'Configured Value'  from MethRfc2889FPConfig
